      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS to achieve its 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory M Variable limited-slip differential. Mechanically, this vehicle is impeccable: the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells, and the VANOS system has been completely overhauled. The suspension retains its factory-correct damping characteristics with fresh bushings throughout, ensuring the chassis remains taut and communicative. This is a turn-key collector-quality vehicle with no deferred maintenance and a comprehensive service history.",
